# m5_p16_weapons_showcase.shot — M5 P16
#
# Cycles five Trooper dummies through five different weapons across the
# weapon-atlas range. Combined with m5_p16_chassis_lineup.shot's four
# additional weapons (Burst SMG / Mass Driver / Rail Cannon / Grappling
# Hook), this hits 9 of the 14 sprites in g_weapon_sprites[]. The
# remaining 5 (Plasma SMG, Sidearm, Frag Grenades, Micro Rockets,
# Combat Knife) have smaller silhouettes that read at the foundry-shot
# zoom too — hitting the most-used 9 weapons is sufficient for ship.
#
# Run:
#   ./soldut --shot tests/shots/m5_p16_weapons_showcase.shot
# Output:
#   build/shots/m5_p16_weapons_showcase/showcase.png
#
# Verification:
#   - the log shows `weapons_atlas: loaded assets/sprites/weapons.png`
#     (1024x256 expected)
#   - 5 visibly different weapon silhouettes in the 5 R_HANDs across
#     the lineup

window 1280 720
seed   11 7
out    build/shots/m5_p16_weapons_showcase

loadout Trooper "Pulse Rifle" "Frag Grenades" Light Standard
spawn_at 1060 984
mouse    640 360

extra_chassis Trooper  740 984 "Riot Cannon"
extra_chassis Trooper  900 984 "Auto-Cannon"
extra_chassis Trooper 1220 984 "Plasma Cannon"
extra_chassis Trooper 1380 984 "Microgun"

at  90 shot showcase
at 120 end
